## Vocabulary contract

| Concept | Correct term | Not |
|---------|-------------|-----|
| TypeScript pass | structural integrity | "types pass" |
| `next build` pass | artifact synthesis | smoke test |
| Tests pass | behavioral integrity | "tests green" |
| knip pass | surface integrity | "no dead code" |
| ESLint pass | doctrine compliance | "lint clean" |
| All checks pass | operational truth coherent | "CI green" |

Words shape architecture culture.
Afenda is not validating files. It is validating **operational truth continuity**.
